### âœ… GitHub Actions CI/CD Pipeline (COMPLETED)
- **Status**: Fully implemented and automated
- **Workflow Files**: 4 comprehensive GitHub Actions workflows
- **Testing**: Automated unit testing on PR creation and merge
- **Building**: Automated executable and installer creation
